A Nigerian soldier cries out after not receiving salary since may. Gistvic Reports. He said alert is one of the things that brings morah to fight as he says they might get sniper soon if nothing is been done. In the video posted, guns were heard coming from houses as the soldiers responded with their fire truck. He wrote: “This people don’t understand that Alert is one of the things that boast Morah to fight..this is June and nothing don happen about MAY…..we go buy sniper o#’ See Photos: Source